OL,3,CMan jailed after ram-raiding a shop
OL,4,Cand stealing more than #3,000 cash
OL,6,FOfficers were called to reports of an
OL,7,Fincident at the Tesco Express store on
OL,8,FNorthwich Road, Weaverham on Monday 16
OL,9,FJune 2025 at around 12.40am.
OL,11,FShortly after the incident, the
OL,12,Fvehicle used during the incident was
OL,13,Flocated in a field in Dutton,
OL,14,FCheshire. The stolen parcels were also
OL,15,Ffound in a nearby pond.
OL,17,FOfficers established that the vehicle
OL,18,Fwas stolen and had been taken from an
OL,19,Faddress in Lancashire in May 2025.
