OL,3,CMan jailed after ram-raiding a shop
OL,4,Cand stealing more than #3,000 cash
OL,6,FRobin Vaughan, from St Helens appeared
OL,7,Fat Chester Crown Court on Tuesday 11
OL,8,FNovember, where he was sentenced to
OL,9,Fthree years in prison.
OL,11,FThe 35-year-old had previously pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty to conspiracy to burgle.
OL,14,FAfter examining CCTV and ANPR footage,
OL,15,Fofficers discovered that the car had
OL,16,Fbeen driven from Merseyside to
OL,17,FWeaverham the night before the robbery
OL,18,Fand had parked on a street near to the
OL,19,FTesco Store.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
