OL,3,CMan jailed after ram-raiding a shop
OL,4,Cand stealing more than #3,000 cash
OL,6,FThe footage showed that the car had
OL,7,Fbeen driven in convoy with a blue Ford
OL,8,FFocus, which had later returned to
OL,9,FMerseyside. The same car returned to
OL,10,FWeaverham on the night of the incident.
OL,12,FRecords showed that the Ford Focus was
OL,13,Fregistered to a woman in Southdene,
OL,14,FKirkby. After identifying the owner of
OL,15,Fthe car, officers arrested Vaughan and
OL,16,Fa 39-year-old woman on Wednesday 8
OL,17,FOctober.
