OL,3,CMan jailed after ram-raiding a shop
OL,4,Cand stealing more than #3,000 cash
OL,6,FDuring questioning Vaughan answered no
OL,7,Fcomment to the questions put to him by
OL,8,Fofficers. Despite his silence, he was
OL,9,Flater charged with one count of
OL,10,Fconspiracy to burgle.
OL,12,FFollowing the sentencing, Police
OL,13,FConstable Dan Lee said: "I welcome the
OL,14,Fprison sentence handed to Vaughan and
OL,15,FI hope it acts as warning to others
OL,16,Fwho are thinking of coming to Cheshire
OL,17,Fto commit crime.
